---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'How secure is our society data?',
    answer: 'We utilize bank-grade 256-bit encryption and ISO-certified data centers. Your community data is siloed and protected by rigorous access control protocols.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What is the process for migrating our existing records?',
    answer: 'Our onboarding concierge handles the entire migration. Simply provide your legacy spreadsheets, and we\'ll map the data to Dwell Hub within 48 hours.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Can residents pay via credit cards?',
    answer: 'Yes, we support all major credit/debit cards, UPI, and net banking. Settlements are typically processed within T+1 working days.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Does Dwell Hub work on mobile devices?',
    answer: 'Absolutely. Dwell Hub works as a Progressive Web App on any browser and also has a dedicated Android app. Add it to your home screen for a native app-like experience.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Who is Dwell Hub designed for?',
    answer: 'Dwell Hub is built for apartment associations, RWAs, and housing society committees that want a premium, clutter-free way to manage dues, records, resident issues, and shared documents.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How do I get started with my society?',
    answer: 'Click "Get Started" and fill in your society details. After setup, you can add blocks, flats, and residents from the dashboard. Our onboarding team is available to assist at every step.',
  },
];
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
    <div class="lg:col-span-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tight mb-6 font-headline">Curated Answers</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body mb-8">Quick resolutions for common resident inquiries regarding our platform and services.</p>
      <a href="#" class="text-primary font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-2 group">
        View full documentation
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-4">
      {faqs.map((faq) => (
        <details class="group bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 open:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            <span>{faq.question}</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm font-body">
            {faq.answer}
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
